\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4.3}{\ignorespaces Evaluation pipeline overview. The top row shows the per-frame baseline path: raw model outputs are filtered (ground-truth validity, confidence, statistical outlier removal), pixel-wise correspondences are established via projection, and Umeyama similarity alignment registers each frame to its ground truth, producing 3D metrics. The bottom row shows the 4D path: the temporal alignment stage of Chapter~\ref {c:methodology} first brings independently reconstructed frames into a shared coordinate system using static masks, after which the concatenated sequence is aligned globally to ground truth to produce 4D metrics.}}{24}{figure.caption.10}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:evaluation_pipeline}{{4.3}{24}{Evaluation pipeline overview. The top row shows the per-frame baseline path: raw model outputs are filtered (ground-truth validity, confidence, statistical outlier removal), pixel-wise correspondences are established via projection, and Umeyama similarity alignment registers each frame to its ground truth, producing 3D metrics. The bottom row shows the 4D path: the temporal alignment stage of Chapter~\ref {c:methodology} first brings independently reconstructed frames into a shared coordinate system using static masks, after which the concatenated sequence is aligned globally to ground truth to produce 4D metrics}{figure.caption.10}{}}
